#treatmentDefinitionsModal(tabindex="-1", role="dialog", aria-labelledby="myModalLabel", aria-hidden="true").modal.fade
  .modal-dialog
    .modal-content
      .modal-header
        button(type="button", data-dismiss="modal").close
          span(aria-hidden="true") &times;
          span.sr-only Close
        h4#myModalLabel.modal-title Concept Definitions

      .modal-body
        .panel
          .panel-body
            p.lead <span style='background-color:rgb(255, 209, 220);'>Treatment</span> concepts include:
            ol(style='margin-left: 8px;').list-unstyled
              li <strong>Drug</strong> – a substance that has biological effects on humans or other animals, and can be at different stages of development and have multiple names
              li <strong>Drug Class</strong> – a specific category of drugs based often (but not always) based on mechanism of action
              p <br>If you suspect an unfamiliar term of being a drug but are unsure, check here: <a href='http://www.drugbank.ca/' target='_blank'>http://www.drugbank.ca/</a> or on Google or Wikipedia (for drugs under development) or or visit our <a href='http://mark2cure.wikia.com/wiki/Board:Treatments_Concept_Help' target='_blank'>new Wikia forum for help</a>

      .modal-footer
        button(type="button", data-dismiss="modal").btn.btn-default Close
